The '''School of Geosciences''' is a constituent body of the [[Sydney Faculty of Science|Faculty of Science]] at the [[University of Sydney]], [[Australia]]. It was established in 1998.
==History== The School was established in 1998 with the merger of the Department of Geology and Geophysics, and the Department of Geography.<ref name="school_hist">http://www.geosci.usyd.edu.au/about_us/au_history.shtml</ref>
